summary: This adds a few more trees and stumps to give Riverwood more of a lumber town feel, while keeping some shade of course. ;)  [There is a file for ETAC (Expanded Towns and Cities)]
descriptionHtml:
I have either hated or loved walking through Riverwood. I've tried multiple mods to give it some variety. Some did too little, and others too much. So I decided to give it a whirl.

I've added a few more trees to give some character and shade to the area. There are also more stumps to reinforce the idea that this is a lumber town. You'll also notice a few added plants, moss and vines as well.

There is also a full version for ETAC (Expanded Towns and Cities) (Which is what I use :D)

PLEASE PLEASE PLEASE Give me feed back, (Please be nice / constructive criticism) I'm a newbie. If there are any suggestions I will gladly consider them. If there are any incompatibilities please let me know, and I will do my very best to resolve them.

Thank you and I hope you enjoy the mod!! :D
author: Skyzr88
